1.0.name: wordpress/bookmark-share-simple
1.0.description: Bookmark, Share, Simple adds a fixed bookmark drawn in HTML5 canvas to the top of your site. When this bookmark is hovered over, it lengthens, and clicking on it displays a share box, which shows 6 icons. When one of these icons is clicked, the sharing service for the appropriate site appears in a popup.
